nce their hardness ratios may be affected by non-nuclear X-ray\nemissions, or are undetected altogether. They require further observations to\nbe fully characterized.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 May 2019 18:00:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 31 Jul 2019 18:00:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-25"}
