planetesimals may grow into carbon-poor rocky planetesimals by\naccreting a large amount of carbon-poor chondrules.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 May 2019 12:27:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-12"}
